<html xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd">
    <body>
        <ol>
            <li>
                <MadCap:snippetText src="task steps/Settings_Downloads.flsnp" />
            </li>
            <li>Click <span class="uicontrol">Download Latest</span> link next to the RADIUS installer that you want to download.</li>
            <li>Use one of the following commands to generate the hash on your local machine. Replace <span class="filepath">setup</span> in the commands with the file path to your downloaded agent.
			<ul><li>Linux: <span class="code">sha512sum setup.rpm</span></li><li>macOS: <span class="code">shasum -a 512 setup.rpm</span></li><li>Windows: <span class="code">CertUtil -hashfile setup.exe SHA512</span></li></ul></li>
            <li>Verify that the generated hash matches the hash on the <span class="wintitle">Downloads</span> page.</li>
        </ol>
    </body>
</html>